ps://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/b7403f10f2892ac2f2f4f09f9635d41043f728d9/libjava%2FChangeLog", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/libjava%2FChangeLog?ref=b7403f10f2892ac2f2f4f09f9635d41043f728d9", "patch": "@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@\n+2002-04-17  Adam King <aking@dreammechanics.com>\n+\n+\t* java/io/File.java (normalizePath): Add Win32 support for auto \n+\tconversion of a '/' path separator to Win32's '\\' separator.\n+\n 2002-04-16  Tom Tromey  <tromey@redhat.com>\n \n \tFix for PR libgcj/6081:"}, {"sha": "2086f1057aa3c06672f11820e1205812c73c8999", "filename": "libjava/java/io/File.java", "status": "modified", "additions": 5, "deletions": 0, "changes": 5, "blob_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/blob/b7403f10f2892ac2f2f4f09f9635d41043f728d9/libjava%2Fjava%2Fio%2FFile.java", "raw_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/b7403f10f2892ac2f2f4f09f9635d41043f728d9/libjava%2Fjava%2Fio%2FFile.java", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/libjava%2Fjava%2Fio%2FFile.java?ref=b7403f10f2892ac2f2f4f09f9635d41043f728d9", "patch": "@@ -82,6 +82,11 @@ public File (String p)\n   // Remove duplicate and redundant separator characters.\n   private String normalizePath(String p)\n   {\n+    // On Windows, convert any '/' to '\\'.  This appears to be the same logic\n+    // that Sun's Win32 Java performs.\n+    if (separatorChar == '\\\\')\n+      p = p.replace ('/', '\\\\');\n+\n     int dupIndex = p.indexOf(dupSeparator);\n     int plen = p.length();\n "}]}